# Walkthrough: Dobot Nova 5 Driver Update for New Firmware

## Summary
Updated the ROS driver to work with the new Dobot controller firmware where **port 30003 (motion) is closed** and all commands go through **port 29999**.

## Changes Made

### 1. [dobot_api.py](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py)
- [DobotApiDashboard](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#54-494) gained all motion methods ([MovJ](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#383-398), [MovL](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup.py#385-390), [JointMovJ](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#533-548), [MoveJog](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#430-446), [Sync](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#668-674), etc.)
- **Command syntax:** [MovJ(pose={x,y,z,rx,ry,rz})](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#383-398), [MovJ(joint={j1,...,j6})](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_api.py#383-398)

### 2. [dobot_bringup.py](file:///home/pi/ros2_ws/src/DOBOT_6Axis_ROS2_V3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup_v3/dobot_bringup.py)
- Removed 30003 retry loop (30s startup delay eliminated)
- `self.move = self.dashboard` — single shared socket

